i-thermochromic pigment yobushushu bepeyinti yemoto yepeyinti yobushushu evuliweyo etshintsha umbala
Igama leMveliso: i-pigment ye-thermochromic
Elinye igama: i-pigment eyenziwe ngubushushu, utshintsho lombala ngebala lobushushu
I-pigment ye-Thermochromic ingasetyenziselwa zonke iintlobo zemigangatho kunye ne-mediums efana nepeyinti, udongwe, iplastiki, i-inki, i-ceramics, ilaphu, iphepha, ifilimu yokwenziwa, iglasi, umbala wokuthambisa, ipolishi yezikhonkwane, i-lipstick, njl njl. i-inki, usety
... 
ekrele okanye nantoni na ocinga ngayo.
Yeplastiki:I-pigment ye-Thermochromic ingasetyenziselwa ukubumba inaliti yeplastiki okanye iimveliso ze-extrusion ezifana ne-PP, i-PU, i-ABS, i-PVC, i-EVA, i-silicone, njl.
Yokwaleka:I-pigment ye-thermochromic ilungele zonke iintlobo zeemveliso zokugquma komhlaba.
Ngee-inki:I-pigment ye-thermochromic ilungele zonke iintlobo zoshicilelo lwemathiriyeli, kubandakanya ilaphu, iphepha, ifilimu yokwenziwa, iglasi, njl.

Kwilinge lokuvala umsantsa wendlala yehlobo, iGalveston County Food Bank iseke inkqubo yeKidz Pacz. Ngexesha leenyanga zasehlotyeni, uninzi lwabantwana abaxhomekeke kukutya simahla okanye kuncitshisiwe esikolweni bahlala besokola ukufumana ukutya okwaneleyo ekhaya. Ngenkqubo yethu ye-Kidz Pacz sibonelela ngokulungele ukutya, iipakethe zokutya ezilungele abantwana kubantwana abafanelekileyo iiveki ezilishumi kwiinyanga zehlobo.

umana i-TEFAP kwaye zihlale eGalveston County. Abantwana kufuneka babe phakathi kweminyaka emithathu ukuya kweli-3 ubudala.
Ndibhalisa njani kwinkqubo yeKidz Pacz?
Jonga zethu imephu interactive phantsi Fumana uNcedo kwiwebhusayithi yethu ukufumana indawo yeKidz Pacz kufutshane nawe. Nceda ufowunele indawo ekuyo ukuqinisekisa indawo yabo yeofisi kunye nenkqubo yobhaliso.

I-pulse oximeter sisixhobo esisetyenziselwa ukulinganisa i-arterial oxygen saturation kwisigulane.Isebenzisa umthombo wokukhanya obandayo okhanya ngencam yomnwe.Emva koko ihlalutya ukukhanya ukumisela ipesenteji yeoksijini kwiiseli ezibomvu zegazi.Isebenzisa olu lwazi ukubala ipesenti yeoksijini esegazini lomntu.Kukho iintlobo ezininzi ze-pulse oximeters.Nantsi inkcazo ekhawulezayo yeziseko ze-pulse oximeters.
I-Pulse oximeters isetyenziswa ngabasebenzi bezempilo ukujonga amanqanaba e-oxygen yes
... 
et yokusetyenziswa kwe-oximeters.I-arhente incoma ukuba iimvavanyo zeklinikhi kufuneka zibandakanye abathathi-nxaxheba abaneentlobo ezahlukeneyo ze-pigmentation yesikhumba.Umzekelo, ubuncinci abathathi-nxaxheba ababini kuphononongo lweklinikhi kufuneka babe nesikhumba esimnyama.Ukuba oku akunakwenzeka, ngoko ke uphononongo lunokufuneka luhlolwe kwakhona, kwaye umxholo woxwebhu lwesikhokelo unokutshintsha.
Ukongeza ekufumaneni i-COVID-19, i-pulse oximeters inokuchonga ezinye iimeko ezichaphazela 
...
o inokunceda izigulana ziqonde amanqanaba e-oxygen yegazi.Enyanisweni, zinengqondo kangangokuba zamkelwa ngokubanzi ngaphambi kokuba ulingo lwenziwe.Ziye zasetyenziswa kwiinkqubo ezahlukeneyo zempilo, kubandakanywa izibhedlele kunye neenkqubo zempilo kumazwe afana neVermont kunye ne-United Kingdom.Abanye bade baba zizixhobo zonyango ezisetyenziswa rhoqo kubaguli emakhayeni abo.Ziluncedo kuxilongo lwe-COVID-19 kwaye ziye zasetyenziswa kulawulo lokhathalelo lwasekhaya.
Ixesha lokuposa: Nov-06-2022

Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo siphawule Ithuba lokuba isiphelo sendlela ephezulu yokusebenza kukaMeizu siza kufika izolo. Oku kwaphikiswa kuba singakhange sibone nasiphi na isenzo sokumiliselwa kunye nokuboniswa kwento enye, esele iqinisekisiwe ukuba iya kuboniswa kwintengiso njenge Meizu 17, into esengqiqweni yokwenza ulandelelwano lomgca, okwangoku okwinombolo ye-16 phantsi kokongezwa okuthile kwigama lokukhetha kuba ineenguqulelo ezininzi emva kwesixhobo sokuqala esifikileyo njenge-Meizu 
... 
ni kwedatha enjalo, ibonisa ngokucacileyo uyilo kunye nobuhle bangaphambili besiphelo sesiphelo esiphakamileyo, ngaloo ndlela ikwangqina oko kwakusele kuvuza ngaphambili.
Ngokwento yokwazisa, eyona siyixhomekeke ngezantsi, I-Meizu 17 iyakwenziwa ngokusemthethweni ngokwe-Epreli 22 ezayoUmhla, ngexesha lokupapashwa kweli nqaku, umalunga neentsuku ezine kude. Ngolo suku siza kuba sazi kwaye siqinisekisa zonke iimpawu kunye nokubalulwa kweselfowuni, kunye nolwazi oluchanekileyo malunga neenguqulelo 
...
neyo. Kananjalo, igcina ukucoceka kunye nokuqaqamba kwe-Meizu 17, inesikrini esigcweleyo esinesakhelo sokukhanya kunye nesibetho esingaphambili esibekwe kugqatso lwepaneli, ebekwe kwikona ephezulu ngasekhohlo.
Ipowusta ayivezi enye inyani ebalulekileyo. Nangona kunjalo, sele sisazi ukuba iMeizu 17 izakubonisa Snapdragon 865, iphaneli ye-OLED engama-90, ukuseta ikhamera ye-quad ngasemva kunye nokutshaja ngokukhawuleza kwe-30 W yenguqulo ye-non-Pro kunye ne-65 W ye-Pro.

Isihluzo esizicocayo sentsimbi esingenasici
1. Inkqubo yolawulo lwezixhobo iyaphendula kwaye ichanekile. Iyakwazi ukulungelelanisa ukungafani koxinzelelo kunye nexesha lokubeka ixabiso ngokwemithombo eyahlukeneyo yamanzi kunye nokuchaneka kokucoca.
2. Into yokucoca ithatha intsimbi yentsimbi engenasici, amandla aphezulu, ubulukhuni obuphezulu, ukunxiba kunye nokumelana nomhlwa, kulula ukuyicoca. Susa ngokulula nangokucokisekileyo ukungcola okubanjelwe sisihluzo sesikrini, ukucoca ngaphandle kweekona ezifileyo.
3. Sisebenzisa i-valve ye-pneumatic, ivule kwaye ivale ngokuzenzekelayo kwaye ixesha lokukhupha lingamiselwa.
4. Uyilo lwesakhiwo sezixhobo zokucoca luhlangene kwaye lunengqiqo, kwaye indawo yomgangatho incinci, kwaye ukufakela kunye nokuhamba kuyaguquguquka kwaye kulula.
5. Inkqubo yombane ithatha imowudi yolawulo edibeneyo, ekwaziyo ukuqaphela ulawulo olukude.
6. Isixhobo esilungisiweyo sinokuqinisekisa ukusebenza kakuhle kokucoca kunye nobomi benkonzo ende.
Amashishini ezicelo
Isihluzo sokuzicoca ngokuyintloko sifanelekile kwishishini lemichiza elungileyo, inkqubo yokucocwa kwamanzi, ukwenza iphepha, ishishini leemoto, ishishini lepetrochemical, umatshini, ukutyabeka kunye namanye amashishini.

I-Tribulus terrestris (yosapho iZygophyllaceae) sisityalo esirhubuluzayo sonyaka esasasazeka e-China, empuma ye-Asiya, kwaye siya kufikelela kwintshona ye-Asiya nakwintshona yeYurophu. Iziqhamo zesi sityalo zisetyenzisiwe kunyango lwesiTshayina lwesiNtu kunyango lwengxaki yamehlo, i-edema, isisu esiswini, uxinzelelo oluphezulu lwegazi, kunye nezifo zentliziyo ngelixa e-India ukusetyenziswa kwayo e-Ayurveda kwakusenzelwa ukungabi namandla, ukungakuthandi ukutya, i-jaundice, ukuphazamiseka kwe-urogenital, kunye nezifo zentliziyo.
I-Tribulus terrestris icetyiswa ikakhulu kwimpilo yamadoda kubandakanya ubungqongqo kunye namandla, ngakumbi ngakumbi ekujonganeni nempilo yentliziyo kunye ne-urogenital. Sisongezo esiqhelekileyo kwiipropathi zayo zokuphucula i-libido kunye neempawu zokunyusa i-testosterone.

E-FONENG, sineqela leengcali ezingama-200 ezinezakhono eziphezulu kunye nabazinikeleyo abasebenza ngokungakhathali ukuyila, ukuphuhlisa, kunye nokuvelisa izincedisi ezikumgangatho ophezulu eziphathwayo.
Sisebenza ngokukhethekileyo ekuveliseni uluhlu olubanzi lweemveliso, kubandakanywa iibhanki zamandla, iitshaja, iintambo, ii-earphone, kunye nezithethi.
Isicwangciso sethu samaxabiso esisempilweni sibonelela abathengi bethu, kubandakanywa abathengisi bevenkile, abasasazi, nabathumeli bangaphandle, ngethuba lokwenza inzuzo entle.
Umbono wethu kunye nomsebenzi wethu kukubonelela ngehlabathi ngezincedisi ezikumgangatho ophezulu.

Ngamanye amaxesha sibhala malunga ilanga, umhlaba nenyanga, kwaye ngokuxhomekeke kumxholo apho sikwenza khona, kufuneka sisebenzise oonobumba abakhulu okanye hayi. Kukho amaxesha apho ootitshala bakuthatha njengokupela gwenxa abanye bengawenzi.
Sifanele silisebenzise nini unobumba omkhulu ukubhekisa kwezi zinto kwaye ngoba?
Ilanga, umhlaba nenyanga
Kwiimeko zeenkwenkwezi, Inyanga kufuneka ibhalwe njengelanga okanye umhlaba, kuba sibhekisa kwezi zinto njengamagama okuyilwa kwezinto ezichaphazelek
... 
zenziwe imali. Umzekelo, kwibinzana elithi "Ndiya elwandle ukuya kutshiswa lilanga," akuyomfuneko ukuba igama "ilanga" lifakwe kwigama elikhulu kuba asibhekiseli kwilanga njengegama eliyiliweyo. Nangona kunjalo, kwibinzana elithi "iiplanethi zijikeleza iLanga", kubalulekile ukuba ibhalwe, kuba sibhekisa kwiLanga njengegama.
Eminye imixholo engeyiyo yeenkwenkwezi
Ngaphandle kwezi meko zeenkwenkwezi, ngokusetyenziswa ngokuthe tye nakwezinye izinto ezivela kwimifanekiso, zibhalwa ngoonobumba abanci
...
hanya kwenyanga, ukutshata, cela inyanga, ilifa lomhlaba kunye nezinye ezifanayo, apho kungekho nto ibalulekileyo enjengeempawu zokucaphula okanye iitekisi ezifunekayo. Umhlaba uhlala ubhalwe ngoonobumba abancinci xa ubhekisa emhlabeni: "Inqwelomoya ingahlala emhlabeni."
Ukuqukumbela singatsho ukuba ngokweenkwenkwezi, iLanga, uMhlaba kunye neNyanga zifakwe kuluhlu kuba ingathi ngamagama abo. Kufana nokubeka igama lakho kumatshini omncinci. Ngale ndlela, ngekhe siphinde senze impazamo xa sibhala.

Ukulungiselela
Gweba itswele kakuhle kakhulu kwaye uyisose epanini ngebhotolo encinci de itswele libonakale. Xa sele ukulungele, yongeza irayisi kwaye uyisuse kubushushu obuphakathi malunga nemizuzu emi-3. Yongeza iwayini emhlophe, kwaye mayinciphise ngokunyusa irayisi ukukhupha isitatshi.
Nje ukuba sibonile ukuba iwayini ikhuphukile, kancinci kancinci kwaye ngaphandle kokuyeka ukuvuselela, sidibanisa umhluzi de sidibanise yonke into, siyivumele ukuba inciphise eminye imizuzu eli-15, ngaphandle kokuyeka ukuvuselela, ide ifunxwe phantse ngokupheleleyo.
Nje ukuba irayisi ilungile, (Siza kubona ukuba ihlala iyisuphu encinci), Yongeza amapere kwizilayi okanye ukunambitha, ngaphambili kususwe ibhotolo encinci epanini ukuyenza ithambe.
Sisusa ngaphezulu kobushushu be risotto kwaye ungeze itshizi inqunyulwe ibe ziingceba kwaye uqhubeke ushukumisa de itshizi ichithe ngokupheleleyo.

Le nto, enokuqulatha amanani kunye neeleta, iya kubekwa phambi kwabazali.
Ngaphakathi kubazali kuya kuba sisiphumo sokwahlula ikota nganye ye-polynomial ngento eqhelekileyo.

un2 + 2ab + b2 = (a + b) usetyenziso2 (isikwere sesixa semigaqo emibini)
un2 - 2ab + b2 = (a - b)2 (isikwere somahluko wamagama amabini)
Ukufumanisa ukuba i-trinomial iyisikwere esifanelekileyo, senza oku kulandelayo:
1) Bala ingcambu yesikwere yemigaqo evela kwisikwere.
2) Phindaphinda amaxabiso afunyenwe ngo-2.
3) Thelekisa ixabiso elifunyenweyo kunye nekota engenazo izikwere. Ukuba bayafana, sisikwere esifanelekileyo.

IINGCEBISO ZONYANGO:
Ukufakwa kwemisonto ye-COG kunokubangela ubomvu, ukudumba, iintlungu okanye ukugruzuka kwindawo yonyango. Ngokwesiqhelo, olu tshintsho luthambile kwaye luyanyamalala emva kweentsuku ezimbalwa. Ukufumana iziphumo ezifanelekileyo zokulungiswa kunye nokuchacha okukhuselekileyo:
-Ungasebenzisi izithambiso ukuya kuthi ga kwiiyure ezili-12
-Thintela i-solarium kunye nokukhanya kakhulu lilanga ukuya kuthi ga kwiiveki ezi-2 emva kwenkqubo
-Ungayichazi indawo yokulungiswa kwindawo ephantsi kakhulu kunye namaqondo aphezulu obushushu
- thambisa ioyile etywina imithambo yegazi kwindawo apho kwenzeke khona ukutyumka

UKULUMKELA:
Imisonto inokusetyenziswa kuphela ngoogqirha kunye nabasebenzi bezonyango abaqeqeshwe kwiindlela zokusebenzisa imisonto yokuphakamisa i-COG. Ngaphambi kokuqala kwenkqubo, kuyacetyiswa ukuba uthathe imbali yezonyango kwaye ufumane imvume yesigulana enolwazi. Inkqubo kunye nendawo yenaliti kufuneka ibe yi-aseptic ngokupheleleyo ngexesha lokumiliselwa. Ngenxa yokunqongophala kwedatha yeklinikhi, ayikhuthazwa into yokuba usebenzise imveliso kwiindawo ezilungisiweyo kunye namanye amalungiselelo nakwindawo ezingacetyiswanga ngumenzi, ngakumbi kwimithambo yegazi, imisipha, imisipha kunye namathambo. Ukungachaneki okanye ukungahambelani neengcebiso zomenzi kunokukhokelela kubunzima nakwiziphumo ebezingalindelekanga.

Imfazwe yaseGonzales - Usuku:
I-Texans kunye namaMexico axabana neGonzales ngo-Oktobha 2, 1835.

Texans

- Amadoda angama-150

Imfazwe yaseGonzales - Imvelaphi:
Ngoxinzelelo lwaluphakama phakathi kwabemi baseTexas kunye nolawulo lwaseMexico lwase-M
... 
kazange afune ukulinda aze azi ukuba akanakuyinyanzela ukuwela e-Gonzales, eCasta√±eda yamkhwelisa amadoda ngo-Oktobha 1 ekukhangela enye inqaba.
Ngaloo busuku bamisa iikhilomitha ezili-7 ukuya kumlambo kwilizwe likaHezekeli Williams. Ngoxa abantu baseMexico bephumla, iiTeans zazisendleleni. Ekhokelwa nguKolonel John Henry Moore, i-Texan militia yawela kwibhantshona entshonalanga yomlambo ize ifike kwikampu yaseMexico.
Imfazwe yaseGonzales - Ukulwa Kuqala:
Ngamandla aseTexas yayingumnxeba owawath
...
huka okucacileyo phakathi kwabahlali baseTexas kunye noRhulumente waseMexico. Xa imfazwe iqalile, imikhosi ye-Texan yahlasela i-Mexican garrisons kwingingqi kwaye yathatha iSan Antonio ngoDisemba. Iimpawu zaza kuhlengahlengiswa kwi- Battle of Alamo , kodwa ekugqibeleni ziza kuzinza ukuzimela kwazo emva kweMfazwe yaseSan Jacinto ngo-Apreli 1836.

Iinkcukacha zeMveliso
Nokuba ufuna ukubeka uhlaza kwibala legalufa elincinci, ikhosi enemingxuma elishumi elinesibhozo, okanye eyakho isiqu sokubeka okuluhlaza ngasemva kweyadi yakho, kukho iindidi ezahlukeneyo zokubeka imifuno ekhoyo ukuze ilingane neemfuno zakho.Ukubeka imifuno yenye yezona ndawo zibaluleke kakhulu kwibala legalufu elipheleleyo, kungakhathaliseki ukuba likhulu okanye lincinci kangakanani.Ayiyiyo yonke into ebeka i-turf eluhlaza eyenziwe ngendlela efanayo, ke iTurf WHDY ithwala iintlobo ngeentlobo zengca eyenziweyo onokuthi ukhethe kuyo.
Enye i-turf eyenziweyo yokubeka imifuno iyatyibilika, evumela ibhola yegalufa ukuba ihambe ngokukhawuleza.Okunye ukubeka i-turf eluhlaza inokwakheka okutyebileyo, okunokuba ngumngeni ngakumbi kumdlali wegalufa.Kuxhomekeke kwinto oyikhangelayo, ungasebenzisa iindidi ezahlukeneyo zengca eyenziweyo ukwenza ikhosi ecela umngeni kubadlali okanye ikhosi elula.

Xa sisiya entsimini okanye sibona iziphene kwindawo, sithetha ngegama lesiqabu. Noko ke, abantu abaninzi abazi yintoni ukukhululeka okanye kweziphi iinkalo ekufuneka zisetyenziselwe ukuba kusenzelwa ntoni kwi-geology. Uncedo luyinto eyimfuneko kakhulu kubomi bomntu kwaye inzululwazi yejoloji iphonononga isiqabu kwiimeko ezininzi.
Ngenxa yesi sizathu, siza kunikezela eli nqaku ukukuxelela ukuba yintoni isiqabu, ziphi iimpawu zayo kunye nokubaluleka kwayo kumntu.

Umgaqo we-Ultrasonic Welding / Theory
Ultrasonic welding, ekwabizwa ngokuba yi-ultrasonic bonding, yinkqubo apho isantya esiphakamileyo (i-ultrasonic) amaza esandi asetyenziswa kwimisebenzi emibini okanye nangaphezulu ebanjwayo kunye phantsi koxinzelelo lokuyifaka kwisiqwenga esinye. Ngokuqhelekileyo kusetyenziswa ukudibanisa iinxalenye zeplastiki-ngakumbi ezo zenziwe ngeentlobo ezahlukeneyo zeplastiki-i-welding ye-ultrasonic ibopha ngokusisigxina imisebenzi eyenziwayo ngaphandle kwemfuneko yoku
... 
 Xa usetyenziswa kwisinyithi, into ephawuleka ngale ndlela kukuba iqondo lobushushu lihlala lingaphantsi komgangatho wokunyibilika kwezixhobo ezichaphazelekayo ukuthintela naziphi na iipropathi ezingafunekiyo ezinokuvela kubushushu obuphezulu bezinto.
Isebenza njani i-welding ye-ultrasonic?
Yonke into eyenziwayo ye-welding ye-ultrasonic iya kwahluka ngokusekwe kwinto yeplastikhi edityanisiweyo, imilo yezinto zokusebenza, kunye nezinye izinto. Nangona kunjalo, inkqubo iyonke iyafana. Amacandelo a
...
mdibaniso apho la macandelo mabini ahlanganisene khona ngokukodwa yenzelwe ukuququzelela ukunyibilika kunye nokudityaniswa kweenkqubo. Emva kokuba iinxalenye zidityaniswe ngokufanelekileyo, ukungcangcazela kuyayeka kwaye iiplastikhi zipholile ngokukhawuleza okukhulu, zenze iqhina elomeleleyo ngokumangalisayo.

Nge-Sep 17, iShuangliang Eco-Energy yaphumelela i-2020 yaseTshayina yahambisa Amandla aGqwesileyo eProjekthi yeBhaso. Lo ngunyaka wesixhenxe ulandelelana ukuba uphumelele ibhaso.
Iprojekthi ezuze amabhaso iShijiazhuang People's Hospital yiCCHP isasaza iprojekthi yamandla esekwe kwirhasi yendalo. Izixhobo ezingundoqo zibandakanya iiseti ezi-2 zeinjini ezivuthayo ze-2MW, i-2 flue gas kunye namanzi ashushu we-LiBr Absorption Chillers, i-3 Centrifugal Chillers, i-3 yamanzi ashushu / i-boilers-fired boilers kunye ne-3 exchange exchange. Ukubonelela ngeenkonzo zamandla esibhedlele ngesipholisa, ukufudumeza, ukuhambisa umbane, amanzi ashushu asekhaya kunye nomphunga wezonyango.
Xa kuthelekiswa nezixhobo zamandla ombane ezisebenza ngombane ezisebenzisa amalahle, igcina i-2974.35t / yamalahle aqhelekileyo ngonyaka, ngereyithi yokonga umbane ye-27%. Unciphiso lonyaka lokukhutshwa kwe-CO‚ÇÇ yi-12156.18t / a, ngezinga lokunciphisa lama-48%, nelinezibonelelo ezingcono kwezoqoqosho nakwezokusingqongileyo.

Yintoni i polyaspartic umgangatho ukutyabeka?
Polyaspartate polyurea ukutyabeka, ekubhekiselwa kuyo njenge polyaspartic umgangatho ukutyabeka, luhlobo olutsha lwe-aliphatic, isantya sokuphendula esilawulekayo (akukho mfuneko yokomisa), ukusebenza okuphezulu (okulingana okanye ngaphezulu kwe-polyurethane yokugquma), ukukhutshwa kwe-VOC ephantsi (umxholo ophezulu oqinileyo kwi-85% -100%), owaziwa ngokuba ngowesithathu. Isizukulwana se-polyurea kushishino lwe-polyurethane kwiminyaka yakutshanje. In
... 
a kuphezulu. Izinga lokugubungela lingcono kunezinye iingubo (ezifana ne-solvent-based-coatings, i-coatings-based-coatings), kunye neengubo eziqhelekileyo zilula ukwenza uluhlu oluncinci, ngaloo ndlela ukuveza i-substrates, echaphazela i-anti-corrosion effect.
Iindleko ezibanzi:
1, Ixabiso le polyaspartic ukutyabeka iphezulu, kodwa umxholo oqinileyo uphezulu kakhulu. Ngokwethiyori iindleko zayo kufuneka zifane ne-solvent-based coating;
I-2, Ukunciphisa iindleko zamandla;
I-3, iindleko zokuthenga
...
kunye nokungathathi hlangothi kwekhabhoni;
Iindleko zotyalo-mali:
I-1, Umgca wokuvelisa okhoyo unokusetyenziswa ngokuthe ngqo, kwaye igumbi lokumisa livaliwe;
I-2, Umgca omtsha wokuvelisa i-coating ungagcina utyalo-mali kwi-coating drying (ukunyanga) izixhobo kunye nendawo yomgangatho weworkshop.
Ubunzima bokuphumeza:ngokwenkqubo efanelekileyo (indlela enamanyathelo amahlanu) ukuvavanya kunye nokutshintsha, kukulungele ngakumbi kunezinye iintlobo zeengubo kwaye kunempembelelo encinci kwimveliso.

Emva kokuba ubhaliso, uzalise imihlaba kwi-inkangeleko yakho, layisha phezulu yakho iifoto, kwaye Dating iwebhusayithi ayisayi kusilela ukuqala yokubhala kuwe yonke imihla kwizithuba ezitsha kunye iziphakamiso Dating ukusuka omnye abafazi kwaye onomdla abantu. Ukuba ngaba ukukhangela enye kubekho inkqubela okanye omnye guy kuba fun kwaye ukudala budlelwane nabanye okanye nje zithungelana kwi-moments ka-sadness, ngaba beza ngenene ekunene site. Ukongeza, ungakhetha naliphi na isixeko ukukhangela amacala iziqu zabo. Ukudityaniswa kwayo kukuzonwabisa kungumxholo oshushu, kunye nabaninzi abanomdla wokuqikelela ukuba iya kuqhubeka nokuguqula ishishini kwaye liyise kumanqanaba angazange abonwe ngaphambili.

...

Khuphela ComboFix
Amandla ayo aphambili asekukwazini kwayo ukubona kunye nokuphelisa izoyikiso ezinokungahoywa zezinye iinkqubo ezimiselweyo ze-antivirus.
Amandla e-ComboFix

ko eqhelekileyo. Yenzelwe abasebenzisi abakhululekileyo kulawulo lwenkqubo kunye nokususwa kwe-malware ngesandla.

Ke ngoko, kuyacetyiswa ukuba usebenzise i-ComboFix phantsi kwesikhokelo sobuchwephesha obuqeqeshiweyo okanye umntu onamava ekusebenziseni kwayo.

Indadi yodumo eywziwayo neyenza ezibukwayo kwiiolimpiki ezigqithileyo Meeks eli loMzantsi Afrika ngempumelelo ukhawuleze waphuma ngethuba ephuma isibini kumgama wekhulu kwibuterfly izolo kwiParis 2024. UChad akalenzanga ixesha kuba ubekwindaeo yamashumi amabini anesine ephosa ukuba kwindawo yeshumi elinesithandathu.
Nangona kunjalo uChad uthi usezakuqhubekeka edada, lo Jackson le Clios ubonakale ebambe igxalaba emva kokugqqiba kwakhe.
Ukhumbule ukuba uChad le Clos noneminyaka engamashumi amathathu anesibini ubudala waphuma kwindawo anesihlanu kumgama wamakhulu amabini kwiButerfly kwiTokyo 2020. Lendadi ibinethemba lokufika kumagqibela kankqoyi kulomgama nanjengoko yaphumelelabkuwo isilivere kwiLondon 2912 nakwiRio 2016.
uChad uthi akanikezeli nangona ebonakala ekwaziva ebethekile ngenxa yomonzakalo emqolo negxalaba ikakhulu.
UChad le Clos usafuna ukubetha uRyan Lochte owafumana iindondo ezingamashumi amabini anesine(24) kuzo wabe ufumane iigolide ezilishumi elinesine(14), kanti tena kule Clos egameni lakhe uneendondo ezilishumi elinethoba(19) ufumene iigolide ezilishumi elinesibini(12)

I-Gooseberries isasazwa kumazwe onke aseYurophu, amazwe aseMntla Melika naseAsia. EYurophu, njengamazwe amaninzi aseYurophu, ukususela ekuqaleni kwekhulu le-17 i-gooseberries yayingumngcele ogqithiseleyo, kodwa ngaphambili wawubizwa ngeendlela ezahlukeneyo-i-bits-cap okanye i-borsen. Ukusuka apha eBersenevskaya emangcwabeni, esiseMoscow sibonga kwintsimi yebhotwe, apho abalimi breden borsen, kwaye bafumana igama layo. Nangona kunjalo, ekuqaleni kwekhulu lama-20, i-gooseberries inesifo-i-spherote
... 
etic, i-diuretic, i-hemostatic, i-anti-inflammatory and restorative effect.
Iziqhamo okanye izithelo ezinjenge-decoction zimiselwe ukuba kukho ukunqongophala kwentsimbi, ubhedu, i-phosphorus emzimbeni, kunye ne-hypovitaminosis, ukuxilongwa okungapheliyo, ukuphuma kwamanzi, kunye neengxaki ezahlukeneyo zesisombululo (ubunzima obukhulu), i-gastroenterocolitis, i-hydrocephalus, izifo zesikhumba, i-beriberi A kunye no-C I-Gooseberries isetyenziselwa ukuqinisa iindonga zemithambo yegazi.

litre amanzi, kunye ne-tip ch. isinamoni (kunye noshukela). Faka i-gooseberry kwi-juicer uze ufumane ijusi. Ijusi ixutywe kunye nejisi lemon, ushukela, isinamoni kunye namanzi ashushu.
I-Gooseberries nge-orange. 1 kilogram ye-gooseberry, 1 i-orange, 1-1, 3 kg. ushukela. Sidlula kwi-grinder ye-gooseberries kunye ne-orange (susa amathambo), yongeza ishukela, xuba kakuhle, udibanise kwiimbiza eziqhekekileyo, uvale kunye ne-plastiki kunye nesitolo kwifriji. Ngako oko, onke amavithamini aya kugcinwa.

Umsebenzi
Iparacetamol powder isondlo supplemen Isetyenziselwa i-amino acid ukumnika, ngenxa yokufuma okukhethekileyo, ikwasetyenziswa nakwikhrim ebandayo, ii-osmetics. I-Serine ibumba umzimba womntu weentlobo ezahlukeneyo ze-amino acid ebalulekileyo yeprotheni, kuba ukwakhiwa kweprotein kunendima ebaluleke kakhulu.
Ukusetyenziswa
IParacetamol yamkelwe ukunciphisa umkhuhlane kubantu bayo yonke iminyaka.
IParacetamol isetyenziselwa ukukhulula iintlungu ezinxulunyaniswa namalungu amaninzi omzimba. Inezinto ezinokuthomalalisa iintlungu xa zithelekiswa nezo ze-aspirin, ngelixa iziphumo zayo ezichasayo zibuthathaka. Kungcono ukunyamezeleka kune-aspirin kwizigulana ekuthi kuzo kugcinwe ukugcwala kwe-gastric acid okanye ukongezwa kwexesha lokuphuma kwegazi kunokuba yinkxalabo.

Amanzi ashushu okanye isicoci eshushu sisetyenziselwa inkqubo yokucoca. Ukujikeleza kwenziwa ngenkqubo yemidlalo eshushu yamakhasethi. Ewe, unyango lweendaba lubalulekile njengesixhobo senkqubo. Umjikelezo ofanelekileyo weendaba awufuni kuphela iitanki, isikhululo sepompo kunye nabatshisi abushushu. Iiyunithi zokucoca, ioyile skimmer kunye ne-demademmer kufuneka zibe yinxalenye yesekethe. Inkqubo yokubonakalayo yanamhlanje ivumela umqhubi ukuba asebenze icandelo lokuhlaziya kwimodi yokuzenzekelayo ngokupheleleyo. Lonke ulwazi olubalulekileyo njengamanqanaba etanki, amaqondo obushushu, umthwalo womsebenzi, izantya zebrashi, njl. Njl ziya kuboniswa kwi-HMI.

IRift Valley Fever (RVF) sisifo esihlasela iigusha, iinkomo kwakunye neebhokhwe apho siye sibangele ukuphunza nokufa kwemfuyo.
Kodwa ingaba sibosulela njani abantu esi sifo? Abantu bangosuleleka yiRVF ngokubamba igazi nezinye iincindi kwisilwanyana esichaphazelekileyo. Abantu abaninzi abachaphazelekileyo babaneempawu zokugula emva kweentsuku ezimbini ukuya kwezintandathu emva kokuba bedibene nencindi okanye igazi lesilwanyana esichaphazelekileyo. Iimpawu zokugula emntwini iba ngumkhuhlane, ukuqa
... 
Umfuyi uza kubuza ukuba angayikhusela njani iRVF. Impendulo: Impahla ephilileyo, engachaphazelekanga ingagonywa ngechiza lokugonyela iRVF, izilwanyana ezingakhulelwanga zingagonywa ngechiza lokugonyela iRVF, izilwanyana ezikhulelweyo okanye ezo zinokuba zikhulelwe, zingagonywa ngeyeza lokugonya ezingekho mandleni okugonya.
Ndingazikhusela njani mna kwiRVF, kubuza umfuyi. Impendulo: Musa ukuzixhela izilwanyana ezigulayo, akuvumelekanga ukutya inyama yezilwanyana ezigulayo, nxiba imaski nezidla za
...
unzileyo, nenyama yayo iphekwe ngokukuko phambi kokuba ityiwe. Ukuba ucinga ukuba ufuna ingcebiso okanye ulwazi oluthe vetshe, ungatsalela ugqirha wezilwanyana wengingqi yakho.
Ukuba ucinga ukuba imfuyo yakho ichaphazelekile, nceda utsalele ugqirha wezilwanyana okanye igosa elijongene nempilo yemfuyo kwingingqi yakho.
Khusela isiqu sakho, usapho lwakho nemfuyo yakho kwiRift Valley Fever. Olu lulwazi olusuka kwiSebe lezoLimo noPhuhliso lwamaPhandle kuZwelonke.

Ngaphandle kokuthathwa njengophelelwe lixesha kwaye "walaliswa ebhedini" bubuchwephesha obutsha, email iseyinto ebalulekileyo kwindlela abantu kunye namashishini abanxibelelana ngayo. Abemi bedijithali ngokwenene basebenzisa izixhobo zokunxibelelana nabantu ezinje nge-Facebook kunye ne-Twitter ukuthumela imiyalezo, kodwa ama-94% abantu baseMelika abaneminyaka eli-12 nangaphezulu- abasebenza kwi-Intanethi bakhetha i-imeyile ngokuchasene nomlinganiso we-140.
Ngenxa yoko, kubaqeqeshi bezentengiso, kukho ukuvumelana okumangalisayo kokuba i-imeyile isesona sixhobo sikhawulezayo nesona sinokuthenjwa ekufumaneni abathengi kunye Nxaxheba. Ngokufikelela okuninzi kunxibelelwano lwasentlalweni, umabonwakude kunye nezinye iindlela ezingenakubalwa ukufikelela kubaphulaphuli babo, iipesenti ezingama-64 zamashishini ziceba ukwandisa utyalo-mali kwintengiso ye-imeyile ngo-2013, ngokutsho Imarketo infographic.
Uninzi lwabathengisi, i-imeyile iya kuqhubeka ixilongo kwezinye iindlela zonxibelelwano kuba ithembekile, ichanekile, isicwangciso-qhinga kwaye ivumela ulungelelwaniso lweendlela ezinqamlezileyo. Awuqinisekanga? Jonga ngakumbi idatha apha:
